{"id":"ZPRAC_CDS_CUSTOM_ENTITY","title":"DDIC data sources with ABAP-based data retrieval","phase":9,"phaseName":"Advanced Data Modeling","category":"Advanced Data Modeling","subcategory":"Custom & Abstract","language":"abap","description":"CDS Custom Entities — Non-DDIC data sources with ABAP-based data retrieval. Key topics: `define custom entity` creates a typed CDS data source without a. `@ObjectModel.query.implementedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_...'` binds the entity to. `define root custom entity` enables full RAP support (transactional.","sections":[{"title":"Key Learning Points","description":"<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>`define custom entity` creates a typed CDS data source without a</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>`@ObjectModel.query.implementedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_...'` binds the entity to</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>`define root custom entity` enables full RAP support (transactional</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>The ABAP class must implement `IF_RAP_QUERY_PROVIDER` for RAP integration</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Method IF_RAP_QUERY_PROVIDER~SELECT( ) receives the request filter,</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Custom entities are ideal for wrapping external APIs (RFC, SOAP, OData),</span></div></div>"},{"title":"Concept Diagram","description":"<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-b\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-p\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#A855F7\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Custom Entity — Data Flow & Implementation</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ DATA FLOW ============ -->\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">End-to-End Data Flow</text>\n\n  <!-- Step 1: External -->\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">1. External Request</text>\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"115\" width=\"130\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"105\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#16A34A\">External Source</text>\n  <text x=\"105\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">BAPI / RFC / Web API</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"170\" y1=\"140\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"140\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <text x=\"190\" y=\"133\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#E95420\">CALL</text>\n\n  <!-- Step 2: Provider Class -->\n  <text x=\"330\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">2. Provider Class</text>\n  <rect x=\"215\" y=\"115\" width=\"240\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"335\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">ABAP Query Provider</text>\n  <text x=\"335\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">IF_RAP_QUERY_PROVIDER~select</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"455\" y1=\"140\" x2=\"495\" y2=\"140\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <text x=\"475\" y=\"133\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#E95420\">MAP</text>\n\n  <!-- Step 3: Custom Entity -->\n  <text x=\"640\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">3. Custom Entity</text>\n  <rect x=\"500\" y=\"115\" width=\"280\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#E0F2FE\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"640\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2563EB\">Custom Entity (CDS)</text>\n  <text x=\"640\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">@ObjectModel.query.implementedBy</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"780\" y1=\"140\" x2=\"820\" y2=\"140\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Step 4: Consumer -->\n  <text x=\"910\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">4. Consumer</text>\n  <rect x=\"825\" y=\"115\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"900\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Consumer</text>\n  <text x=\"900\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">OData / Fiori / ABAP</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ CDS DEFINITION ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"190\" width=\"920\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"212\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#22C55E\">Custom Entity — CDS Definition</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"234\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@ObjectModel.query.implementedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_PRAC_PURCHASE_QUERY'</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"251\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\">define root view entity ZPRAC_CDS_C_PurchaseOrder</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"268\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  as select from <tspan fill=\"#EF4444\" font-weight=\"bold\">???</tspan>   <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- No FROM clause — data comes from ABAP provider</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"285\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">{ key PurchaseOrder: abap.char(10); CompanyCode: abap.char(4); ... }</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ PROVIDER CLASS ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"305\" width=\"450\" height=\"200\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"265\" y=\"328\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">ABAP Provider Class Implementation</text>\n  <line x1=\"55\" y1=\"335\" x2=\"475\" y2=\"335\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"355\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">CLASS ZCL_PRAC_PURCHASE_QUERY IMPLEMENTATION.</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"372\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">  METHOD if_rap_query_provider~select.</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#E95420\">    \" 1. Read parameters</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"409\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">    DATA(lt_filter) = io_request-&gt;get_filter( ).</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"426\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#E95420\">    \" 2. Call external source</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"443\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">    DATA(lt_data) = call_bapi( lt_filter ).</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"460\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#E95420\">    \" 3. Return data</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"477\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">    io_response-&gt;set_total_number_of_records( </text>\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"494\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">      lines( lt_data ) ).</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"505\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">    io_response-&gt;set_data( lt_data ).</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ KEY METHODS ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"305\" width=\"450\" height=\"200\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"735\" y=\"328\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">IF_RAP_QUERY_PROVIDER Interface Methods</text>\n  <line x1=\"525\" y1=\"335\" x2=\"945\" y2=\"335\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"358\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">io_request methods:</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"380\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">get_filter( )  → Return filter conditions</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"398\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">get_paging( )  → Offset + page size</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"416\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">get_sort( )    → Sort order elements</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"434\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">get_requested_elements( )  → Selected fields</text>\n\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"462\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">io_response methods:</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"484\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">set_data( it_data )  → Return result table</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"502\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">set_total_number_of_records( iv_count )  → Total rows</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ USE CASES ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"520\" width=\"920\" height=\"210\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"543\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">When to Use Custom Entities</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"550\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"550\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"60\" y=\"565\" width=\"280\" height=\"75\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"585\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">External Data Integration</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"603\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">BAPI calls, Web services,</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"621\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">RFC-enabled function modules</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"360\" y=\"565\" width=\"280\" height=\"75\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"585\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">Complex Business Logic</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"603\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Multi-step calculations,</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"621\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">conditional aggregations</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"660\" y=\"565\" width=\"280\" height=\"75\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"585\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Legacy System Access</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"603\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Read from non-HANA sources,</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"621\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">CDS views not possible</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"655\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"655\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"680\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">⚠ Custom entities have <tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EF4444\">no SELECT</tspan> from a database table — the FROM clause is absent.</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"700\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">⚠ All data is provided by the ABAP query provider class — you must implement filter/sort/paging yourself.</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"720\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">⚠ Association to custom entities is possible but the target cannot use path expressions (no automatic JOIN).</text>\n<text x=\"10\" y=\"20\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(233,84,32,0.15)\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">cds-bytes (c) 2026</text></svg></div>"},{"title":"CDS Source Code","language":"abap","codeBlock":"/*\n * ====================================================================\n * CDS — Custom Entity for Purchase Order (Conceptual)\n * ====================================================================\n */\n\n@EndUserText.label: 'Custom Entity — Purchase Order Data'\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED\n\n@ObjectModel.query.implementedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_PRAC_PURCHASE_QUERY'\n\ndefine root custom entity ZPRAC_CDS_C_PurchaseOrder\n{\n  key PurchaseOrder  : abap.char(10);\n      CompanyCode    : abap.char(4);\n      Supplier       : abap.char(10);\n      GrossAmount    : abap.curr(15,2);\n      Currency       : abap.char(5);\n      CreatedBy      : abap.char(12);\n      CreatedAt      : abap.dec(15,0);\n}\nwith parameters\n  @Environment.systemField: #SYSTEM_DATE\n  p_cutoff_date : abap.dats\n\n/*\n * ====================================================================\n * ABAP Class — Query Provider Implementation\n * ====================================================================\n */\n\nCLASS zcl_prac_purchase_query DEFINITION PUBLIC FINAL CREATE PUBLIC.\n  PUBLIC SECTION.\n    INTERFACES if_rap_query_provider.\nENDCLASS.\n\nCLASS zcl_prac_purchase_query IMPLEMENTATION.\n\n  METHOD if_rap_query_provider~select.\n    \" Retrieve filter, paging, and request context.\n    DATA(request_filter) = io_request->get_filter( ).\n    DATA(paging)         = io_request->get_paging( ).\n    DATA(cutoff_date)    = io_request->get_parameters( )->get( `P_CUTOFF_DATE` ).\n\n    \" Simulate / API call to fetch purchase order data.\n    \" In production this would call an external OData / RFC / BAPI.\n    DATA(purchase_orders) = VALUE ztab_purchase_order( ).\n    \" ... external API call goes here ...\n\n    \" Apply client-side filter (if the API cannot handle it).\n    IF request_filter IS NOT INITIAL.\n      DATA(filtered_data) = request_filter->apply( purchase_orders ).\n    ENDIF.\n\n    \" Apply paging.\n    DATA(offset) = paging->get_offset( ).\n    DATA(page_size) = paging->get_page_size( ).\n    IF page_size = if_rap_query_paging=>page_size_unlimited.\n      io_response->set_total_number_of_records( lines( filtered_data ) ).\n      io_response->set_data( filtered_data ).\n    ELSE.\n      DATA(paged_data) = filtered_data.\n      \" … apply offset & page_size slicing …\n      io_response->set_total_number_of_records( lines( filtered_data ) ).\n      io_response->set_data( paged_data ).\n    ENDIF.\n  ENDMETHOD.\n\nENDCLASS."}],"content":"<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_CUSTOM_ENTITY-key-learning-points\">Key Learning Points</h2>\n<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>`define custom entity` creates a typed CDS data source without a</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>`@ObjectModel.query.implementedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_...'` binds the entity to</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>`define root custom entity` enables full RAP support (transactional</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>The ABAP class must implement `IF_RAP_QUERY_PROVIDER` for RAP integration</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Method IF_RAP_QUERY_PROVIDER~SELECT( ) receives the request filter,</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Custom entities are ideal for wrapping external APIs (RFC, SOAP, OData),</span></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_CUSTOM_ENTITY-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-b\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-p\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#A855F7\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Custom Entity — Data Flow & Implementation</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ DATA FLOW ============ -->\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">End-to-End Data Flow</text>\n\n  <!-- Step 1: External -->\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">1. External Request</text>\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"115\" width=\"130\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"105\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#16A34A\">External Source</text>\n  <text x=\"105\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">BAPI / RFC / Web API</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"170\" y1=\"140\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"140\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <text x=\"190\" y=\"133\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#E95420\">CALL</text>\n\n  <!-- Step 2: Provider Class -->\n  <text x=\"330\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">2. Provider Class</text>\n  <rect x=\"215\" y=\"115\" width=\"240\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"335\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">ABAP Query Provider</text>\n  <text x=\"335\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">IF_RAP_QUERY_PROVIDER~select</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"455\" y1=\"140\" x2=\"495\" y2=\"140\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <text x=\"475\" y=\"133\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#E95420\">MAP</text>\n\n  <!-- Step 3: Custom Entity -->\n  <text x=\"640\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">3. Custom Entity</text>\n  <rect x=\"500\" y=\"115\" width=\"280\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#E0F2FE\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"640\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2563EB\">Custom Entity (CDS)</text>\n  <text x=\"640\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">@ObjectModel.query.implementedBy</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"780\" y1=\"140\" x2=\"820\" y2=\"140\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Step 4: Consumer -->\n  <text x=\"910\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">4. Consumer</text>\n  <rect x=\"825\" y=\"115\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"900\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Consumer</text>\n  <text x=\"900\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">OData / Fiori / ABAP</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ CDS DEFINITION ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"190\" width=\"920\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"212\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#22C55E\">Custom Entity — CDS Definition</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"234\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@ObjectModel.query.implementedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_PRAC_PURCHASE_QUERY'</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"251\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\">define root view entity ZPRAC_CDS_C_PurchaseOrder</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"268\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  as select from <tspan fill=\"#EF4444\" font-weight=\"bold\">???</tspan>   <tspan fill=\"#64748B\">-- No FROM clause — data comes from ABAP provider</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"285\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">{ key PurchaseOrder: abap.char(10); CompanyCode: abap.char(4); ... }</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ PROVIDER CLASS ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"305\" width=\"450\" height=\"200\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"265\" y=\"328\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">ABAP Provider Class Implementation</text>\n  <line x1=\"55\" y1=\"335\" x2=\"475\" y2=\"335\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"355\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">CLASS ZCL_PRAC_PURCHASE_QUERY IMPLEMENTATION.</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"372\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">  METHOD if_rap_query_provider~select.</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#E95420\">    \" 1. Read parameters</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"409\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">    DATA(lt_filter) = io_request-&gt;get_filter( ).</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"426\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#E95420\">    \" 2. Call external source</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"443\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">    DATA(lt_data) = call_bapi( lt_filter ).</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"460\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#E95420\">    \" 3. Return data</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"477\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">    io_response-&gt;set_total_number_of_records( </text>\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"494\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">      lines( lt_data ) ).</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"505\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">    io_response-&gt;set_data( lt_data ).</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ KEY METHODS ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"305\" width=\"450\" height=\"200\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"735\" y=\"328\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">IF_RAP_QUERY_PROVIDER Interface Methods</text>\n  <line x1=\"525\" y1=\"335\" x2=\"945\" y2=\"335\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"358\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">io_request methods:</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"380\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">get_filter( )  → Return filter conditions</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"398\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">get_paging( )  → Offset + page size</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"416\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">get_sort( )    → Sort order elements</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"434\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">get_requested_elements( )  → Selected fields</text>\n\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"462\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">io_response methods:</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"484\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">set_data( it_data )  → Return result table</text>\n  <text x=\"545\" y=\"502\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">set_total_number_of_records( iv_count )  → Total rows</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ USE CASES ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"520\" width=\"920\" height=\"210\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"543\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">When to Use Custom Entities</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"550\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"550\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"60\" y=\"565\" width=\"280\" height=\"75\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"585\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">External Data Integration</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"603\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">BAPI calls, Web services,</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"621\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">RFC-enabled function modules</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"360\" y=\"565\" width=\"280\" height=\"75\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"585\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">Complex Business Logic</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"603\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Multi-step calculations,</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"621\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">conditional aggregations</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"660\" y=\"565\" width=\"280\" height=\"75\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"585\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Legacy System Access</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"603\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Read from non-HANA sources,</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"621\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">CDS views not possible</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"655\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"655\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"680\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">⚠ Custom entities have <tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EF4444\">no SELECT</tspan> from a database table — the FROM clause is absent.</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"700\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">⚠ All data is provided by the ABAP query provider class — you must implement filter/sort/paging yourself.</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"720\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">⚠ Association to custom entities is possible but the target cannot use path expressions (no automatic JOIN).</text>\n<text x=\"10\" y=\"20\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(233,84,32,0.15)\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">cds-bytes (c) 2026</text></svg></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_CUSTOM_ENTITY-cds-source-code\">CDS Source Code</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-abap\">/*\n * ====================================================================\n * CDS — Custom Entity for Purchase Order (Conceptual)\n * ====================================================================\n */\n\n@EndUserText.label: 'Custom Entity — Purchase Order Data'\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED\n\n@ObjectModel.query.implementedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_PRAC_PURCHASE_QUERY'\n\ndefine root custom entity ZPRAC_CDS_C_PurchaseOrder\n{\n  key PurchaseOrder  : abap.char(10);\n      CompanyCode    : abap.char(4);\n      Supplier       : abap.char(10);\n      GrossAmount    : abap.curr(15,2);\n      Currency       : abap.char(5);\n      CreatedBy      : abap.char(12);\n      CreatedAt      : abap.dec(15,0);\n}\nwith parameters\n  @Environment.systemField: #SYSTEM_DATE\n  p_cutoff_date : abap.dats\n\n/*\n * ====================================================================\n * ABAP Class — Query Provider Implementation\n * ====================================================================\n */\n\nCLASS zcl_prac_purchase_query DEFINITION PUBLIC FINAL CREATE PUBLIC.\n  PUBLIC SECTION.\n    INTERFACES if_rap_query_provider.\nENDCLASS.\n\nCLASS zcl_prac_purchase_query IMPLEMENTATION.\n\n  METHOD if_rap_query_provider~select.\n    \" Retrieve filter, paging, and request context.\n    DATA(request_filter) = io_request->get_filter( ).\n    DATA(paging)         = io_request->get_paging( ).\n    DATA(cutoff_date)    = io_request->get_parameters( )->get( `P_CUTOFF_DATE` ).\n\n    \" Simulate / API call to fetch purchase order data.\n    \" In production this would call an external OData / RFC / BAPI.\n    DATA(purchase_orders) = VALUE ztab_purchase_order( ).\n    \" ... external API call goes here ...\n\n    \" Apply client-side filter (if the API cannot handle it).\n    IF request_filter IS NOT INITIAL.\n      DATA(filtered_data) = request_filter->apply( purchase_orders ).\n    ENDIF.\n\n    \" Apply paging.\n    DATA(offset) = paging->get_offset( ).\n    DATA(page_size) = paging->get_page_size( ).\n    IF page_size = if_rap_query_paging=>page_size_unlimited.\n      io_response->set_total_number_of_records( lines( filtered_data ) ).\n      io_response->set_data( filtered_data ).\n    ELSE.\n      DATA(paged_data) = filtered_data.\n      \" … apply offset & page_size slicing …\n      io_response->set_total_number_of_records( lines( filtered_data ) ).\n      io_response->set_data( paged_data ).\n    ENDIF.\n  ENDMETHOD.\n\nENDCLASS.</code></pre>","tags":["cds-views"],"details":"<p class=\"mb-2\">corresponding database table or DDIC structure — purely definitional.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">an ABAP class that provides the data at runtime.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">behaviour, draft, etc.) — without `root` only read access is possible.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">or `IF_SADL_QUERY_PROVIDER` for plain CDS consumption.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">sorting, and paging and must return data as an internal table.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">calling BAPIs, aggregating disparate data sources, or any logic that</p><p class=\"mb-2\">cannot be expressed in standard SQL.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">COMPARISON: Custom Entity vs Table Function vs Virtual Element</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Feature                | Custom Entity              | Table Function            | Virtual Element</p><p class=\"mb-2\">---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Base object            | CDS definition only        | AMDP / HANA function      | CDS projection view</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Data source            | Any ABAP logic / API       | HANA SQLScript / SQL      | Same DB table as parent</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Code pushdown          | No (ABAP layer)            | Yes (HANA layer)          | No (ABAP layer)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">RAP transactional      | Yes (define root)          | No (read-only)            | Yes (in RAP projection)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DDL / DML support      | No (cannot INSERT/SELECT)  | SELECT only               | No (computed only)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Parameter support      | Yes (CDS parameters)       | No                        | No</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Association target     | Yes                        | Yes                       | Yes</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Use case               | External API, BAPI, RFC    | High-performance SQL algo | Simple ABAP enrichment</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DIAGRAM: assets/diagrams/custom-entity-flow.svg</p>","cdsViewName":"ZPRAC_CDS_CUSTOM_ENTITY","sqlViewName":"","topic":"define custom entity for external data, APIs, and complex logic"}